'<h1>Welcome to Epic: Program for Integrated Circuits</h1>

<p>Epic: Program for Integrated Circuits is a program to create, layout and simulate digital integrated circuits.</p>

<p>It provides more than 25 different components, from simple AND-Gates to complex Graph Visualisers, to allow the user to create circuits without limitations.</p>

<p>EPIC features a fully drag-and-drop based system to make creating circuits intuitive and easy to use. The workflow is furthermore complemented by quickaccess of important features via keyboard shortcuts and a yellow-click (right-click) options menu.</p>' )